{"id": 690, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得新时代的“女人味”应该是什么样的？", "description": "我们曾经调查过，男子气概在新时代的表现是“多做事，少说话”，那现如今的女人味或者女子气概是什么样的？", "record_count": 6781, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194616c1UNCle4gYsVIxqL.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-10T12:38:30Z", "options": [{"id": 33280, "content": "即使一个人也可以生活的很好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120412}, {"id": 44545, "content": "会思考，理性，真正意义上的做到男女平等", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290302}, {"id": 33540, "content": "保持自己的本心，优雅并快乐着活着，不把男人作为生活的唯一", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352300}, {"id": 33287, "content": "能养家能持家", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335373}, {"id": 33288, "content": "有卓然于他人的气质", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347143}, {"id": 33289, "content": "不矫柔做作", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349464}, {"id": 35337, "content": "新时代的女人味应该是 没有女人味！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133181}, {"id": 33290, "content": "做自己 有自己的朋友圈 给对方足够的空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263257}, {"id": 33291, "content": "就算失去了整个世界 也不随意丢弃自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325146}, {"id": 33293, "content": "首先，本着女人是水，对老公尊重的前提下。更要懂得爱护自己。让自己外在要美，内在要丰富。能自己给自己幸福，更能让男人觉得在你能独立的基础上，他又是你的靠山，你毕竟是似水的女人，需要他的臂膀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335822}, {"id": 33294, "content": "有气质 有思想 懂得坚强 懂得示弱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348041}, {"id": 337935, "content": "成熟，风情万种，内有方寸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631238}, {"id": 33551, "content": "想起孔庆东对做人的形容，做一块豆腐，方正洁白，可荤可素。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352403}, {"id": 33807, "content": "我就静静的看着你们装b", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 318532}, {"id": 34064, "content": "母爱泛滥，坚强独立。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 356922}, {"id": 33297, "content": "不会总以自己的女性身份为自己谋特权。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 329377}, {"id": 33300, "content": "文艺知性", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348213}, {"id": 33302, "content": "可以很傻，但却举止间散发出温柔", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349599}, {"id": 34838, "content": "多说话 少做事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 362940}, {"id": 33303, "content": "有独特的见解，有自己的主见", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333694}, {"id": 33304, "content": "有脑子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341458}, {"id": 33305, "content": "张曼玉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246588}, {"id": 34074, "content": "需要其担当时不会以“你是男人”而拒绝，有便利可图时不会以“我是女人”而争夺", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358011}, {"id": 33307, "content": "对生活有自己的想法，而不是被别人安排。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256412}, {"id": 33308, "content": "心中有爱，保持犀利", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168505}, {"id": 33309, "content": "天呐一路连点了几个屏的赞 我司读者价值观real正", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 26306}, {"id": 176414, "content": "努力，乐观，独立，永远对明天充满期待。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807816}, {"id": 33311, "content": "大和抚子", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349705}, {"id": 34086, "content": "坚强，独立，自信，有趣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358069}, {"id": 33320, "content": "温柔是最重要的，没有之一。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349719}, {"id": 33321, "content": "用自己的态度包容生活中的一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349720}, {"id": 35625, "content": "所谓的一系列一模一样的网红锥子脸真让人厌烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292692}, {"id": 33322, "content": "跟我一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178601}, {"id": 33323, "content": "拥有女神和女汉子双重人格", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219212}, {"id": 33579, "content": "善良勇敢，内心坚韧；见解独到，和而不同…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352544}, {"id": 33837, "content": "经济思想皆独立  心怀感恩仁慈爱人之心  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355104}, {"id": 176687, "content": "内心强大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958355}, {"id": 33328, "content": "有一点爱好 有一点钱 看一点书 走一点世界 知道爱 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349751}, {"id": 33330, "content": "为什么不开个新时代男人味的讨论版", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337221}, {"id": 35378, "content": "能干（涉及内容太多我就不详细解说了）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281714}, {"id": 33844, "content": "自己有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355172}, {"id": 33339, "content": "思想纯洁却能打败各种流氓，外在温柔却能行事果断。会撒娇却不做作，会卖萌却不泛滥。贴心，实心，真心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046034}, {"id": 35387, "content": "我？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148667}, {"id": 33853, "content": "单身主义", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355218}, {"id": 36669, "content": "美丽的脖子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 383472}, {"id": 33344, "content": "想我冷艳 还想我轻佻又下贱", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222142}, {"id": 34880, "content": "长得可爱就显得讲话有道理。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 34369, "content": "不知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360552}, {"id": 33348, "content": "温婉妩媚小女人，处变不惊大女人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338358}, {"id": 33357, "content": " *´∀`)´∀`)*´∀`)*´∀`) ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4119}]}